{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Lost Sheep</strong> is a third-person exploration game that tells two parallel stories: a lost sheep searching for its way home, and a man seeking to rebuild his life and find forgiveness for his past. Players take control of the sheep on a heartfelt journey through beautiful landscapes, uncovering fragments of the man\u2019s story along the way. As the paths of the sheep and the man intertwine, the game explores themes of hope, redemption, and the search for a guiding light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At its core, <strong>The Lost Sheep</strong> is a story about finding peace and purpose through the love and forgiveness of God. Inspired by timeless values and narratives, it offers players a chance to reflect on the profound impact of faith in moments of darkness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298350/extras/GifTLS.gif?t=1732879446\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> For fans of The First Tree, Journey, Firewatch and Shelter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Not a &quot;sheep simulator&quot; but an emotional, intimate story by a on-man team with an ending you won't soon forget.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Featuring a gorgeous soundtrack by acclaimed artists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A short game (about an hour and a half) focused on story with some light puzzle solving and plataforming. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Supports a fan-translation system for subtitles (see Steam forums for details).</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732879446","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298350/page.bg.jpg?t=1732879446","capsule_image":"https://shared.