rst Tree, Journey, Firewatch and Shelter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Not a &quot;sheep simulator&quot; but an emotional, intimate story by a on-man team with an ending you won't soon forget.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Featuring a gorgeous soundtrack by acclaimed artists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A short game (about an hour and a half) focused on story with some light puzzle solving and plataforming. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Supports a fan-translation system for subtitles (see Steam forums for details).</p></li></ul>","developers":["Joan Sab\u00e9 Mart\u00ednez"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298350/header.jpg?t=1732879446","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> High Sierra 10.13+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> X64 architecture with SSE2 instruction set support<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Metal-capable Intel and AMD GPUs<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257077623,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257077623/movie480.mp4?t=1732874301","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257077623/movie_max.mp4?t=1732874301"},"name":"Official Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257077623/57b473ed8a67ae42d3b5a017eeeeec188ea04963/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1732874301","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257077623/movie480_vp9